  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/50px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/75px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/100px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Prince</span><br />Qyle Martell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/50px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/75px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/100px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Coryanne_and_Qyle_Martell_by_Martina_Fackova_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Coryanne and Qyle Martell by Martina Fackova (The Rise of the Dragon).jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ef/Coryanne_and_Qyle_Martell_by_Martina_Fackova_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/250px-Coryanne_and_Qyle_Martell_by_Martina_Fackova_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"213\" srcset=\"/images/e/ef/Coryanne_and_Qyle_Martell_by_Martina_Fackova_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Qyle Martell with his sister, Coryanne Martell by Martina Fačková for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Prince\" title=\"Prince\">Prince</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_116_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">116</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Qyle Nymeros Martell</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dornish</a> prince and younger brother to Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Aliandra_Martell\" title=\"Aliandra Martell\">Aliandra Martell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qyle_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Prince Qyle was a son of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren Martell</a>. His elder sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Aliandra_Martell\" title=\"Aliandra Martell\">Aliandra</a> became <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a> after their father's death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> suggested Qyle as a possible husband for Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela Targaryen</a> and father of a potential male heir to the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>, but he was soon dismissed. Baela was instead arranged to marry Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Thaddeus_Rowan\" title=\"Thaddeus Rowan\">Thaddeus Rowan</a>, though she broke the betrothal by marrying Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a> without the consent of the council.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Qyle and his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Coryanne_Martell\" title=\"Coryanne Martell\">Coryanne</a> were later angered by the attentions the flirtatious Aliandra lavished upon Lord Alyn when he came to <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qyle_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: